      <Value><![CDATA[Liza I. Dadone, Kevin K. Haussler, Greg Brown, Melanie Marsden, James Gaynor, Matthew S. Johnston, and DellaGarelle (2013) SUCCESSFUL MANAGEMENT OF ACUTE-ONSET TORTICOLLIS IN A GIRAFFE (GIRAFFA CAMELOPARDALIS RETICULATA). Journal of Zoo and Wildlife Medicine: March 2013, Vol. 44, No. 1, pp. 181-185.]]></Value>
    </articleReference>
    <articleTitle>
      <Value><![CDATA[Successful management of acute-onset torticollis in a giraffe]]></Value>
